body_html:
@zycdragonball there are failures in the cmake build, that all look like this:

11:09:16 ImportError: No module named 'tensorflow.contrib.repeat.python'

This usually happens when you don't add the repeat module in the tf_python cmake build file.
body:
@zycdragonball there are failures in the cmake build, that all look like this:

```
11:09:16 ImportError: No module named 'tensorflow.contrib.repeat.python'
```

This usually happens when you don't add the repeat module in the tf_python cmake build file.
